data.description: Move-in ready! This end-unit townhome is a rare find in Kent. Close to everything yet with its own private backyard. It boasts modern updates, including a new roof and a stylish kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Experience the perfect balance of convenience and tranquility in this charming retreat, complete with in-unit laundry and two parking spaces. Low dues and easy access to Highways 516, 18, and 167.
